    <item>
      <title>美国银行准备迎接消费者金融数据共享的新时代</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/us-banks-prepare-for-new-era-of-consumer-financial-data-sharing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高消费者监管机构最终确定了一项期待已久的规则，旨在促进金融产品竞争。此后，美国银行必须允许客户访问自己的财务数据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/us-banks-prepare-for-new-era-of-consumer-financial-data-sharing</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球债券市场抛售持续，欧洲股市下跌，SAP 表现亮眼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/european-stocks-steady-amid-global-bond-selloff-sap-shines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储降息预期降温，欧洲股市周二下跌，因欧洲股市周二忙于发布财报，且全球债券抛售进一步扩大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/european-stocks-steady-amid-global-bond-selloff-sap-shines</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 07:10:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储关注美国交易期间日元出现抛售趋势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/yen-selling-set-to-intensify-during-north-american-trading-hours</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博新闻分析显示，当北美交易员上线时，日元兑美元的抛售往往会加剧，这表明日元最大的卖空交易来自何处。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/yen-selling-set-to-intensify-during-north-american-trading-hours</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 06:07:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员重新考虑美联储降息路径，全球债券市场暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/bonds-are-selling-off-everywhere-as-traders-trim-rate-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者考虑美国降息步伐放缓的前景，债券市场延续周一的大幅下跌，这一趋势有可能颠覆各地的债务状况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/bonds-are-selling-off-everywhere-as-traders-trim-rate-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 02:22:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员权衡中东冲突和美联储降息前景 油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-october-22</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商继续关注中东地区以色列和伊朗之间的紧张局势，同时在对美国利率走势的猜测中，更广泛的金融市场呈现避险基调，油价在周一上涨近 2% 之后又出现上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-october-22</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 23:25:48 GMT</pubDate>
